com.epoch.translations

Class QTranslns

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.epoch.translations.QTranslns
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    QuestionConstants, XMLConstants

    public class QTranslns
extends Object
implements QuestionConstants
    Stores all of the translations of the components of a question. Used in question import.
